      "fengshui-career-section": {
        "type": "fengshui-career-section",
        "settings": {
          "title": "Golden  Career  ascension  grid",
          "bg_color": "#f9f5f0",
          "content_image": "shopify://shop_images/8.png",
          "content_text": "<p><strong>Center:</strong> <br/>Position the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Compass Sand Tray</em></span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"> </span>at the center of your desk or shelf. This acts as a powerful foundation, grounding your intentions and harmonizing the energies around you.</p><p><strong>Northwest (Career & Mentors): </strong>Carefully<br/>place the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>BrassAbacus</em></span><em> </em>in the Northwest sector of the sand tray. This strategic positioning catalyzes career advancement, enhances resource management skills, and fosters invaluable<br/>connections.</p><p><strong>Southeast (Wealth):</strong><br/>Place the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Golden<br/>Abundance Vase</em></span> in the Southeast sector of the tray, filling it with clean water or rice. This attracts and cultivates an<br/>abundant flow of wealth energy.</p><p><strong>Core Wealth Activation:</strong><br/>Prominently display the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Gold Ingot(s)</em></span> in the central area of the sand tray.<br/>This powerful symbol actively manifests abundant wealth and firmly anchors<br/>prosperity within your harmonized space.</p><p><strong>Activation:</strong> Engage with your setup daily by gently moving the beads on the abacus and visualizing your financial gains and successes. Ensure the crystal vase remains clean and invigorated, amplifying its energy.</p><p><strong>Essence: </strong>The <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Compass Sand Tray</em></span> harmonizes your environment, the<br/>Northwest Abacus drives you towards career success through insightful<br/>strategies, the Southeast Crystal Vase magnetizes wealth, and the central Gold<br/>Ingot embodies core abundance. Together, these elements create a compelling field of focused energy that empowers your journey towards prosperity and professional excellence.</p>"
        }
      },
      "fengshui-celestial-section": {
        "type": "fengshui-celestial-section",
        "settings": {
          "title": "Harmony & Protection Formation",
          "bg_image": "shopify://shop_images/bj.jpg",
          "content": "<p><strong>Foundation:</strong> Place the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Bagua Sand Tray </em></span>centrally on a stable surface, such as a<br/>living room shelf or console. This positioning creates a harmonized energy grid<br/>for your home.</p><p></p><p><strong>Southwest (Relationships & Love): </strong>Position<br/>the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Pink<br/>Glazed Peach Blossom Incense Holder</em></span><br/>in the tray's Southwest sector. Regularly burn mild floral incense in this area<br/>to nurture loving communication and strengthen family bonds.</p><p></p><p><strong>Center (Grounding & Purification): </strong>Place<br/>the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Pure<br/>Amplifier Crystal</em></span> in the central zone of the tray.<br/>This crystal emits pure energy that clears negativity, promotes calmness, and<br/>stabilizes the home's core atmosphere.</p><p></p><p><strong>Northwest (Mentors & Protection):</strong><br/>Place the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Brass<br/>Calabash</em></span> in the tray's Northwest sector.<br/>Positioned here on the Bagua grid, it actively absorbs and neutralizes negative<br/>energy and potential conflicts within the home's energy field, safeguarding<br/>harmony and supporting the household head.</p><p></p><p><strong>Essence: </strong>The Bagua tray serves to integrate<br/>and harmonize your space. The incense in the Southwest sector fosters<br/>relationship harmony, the central Calcite purifies and grounds the core energy,<br/>and the Brass Gourd in the Northwest protects by dissolving internal discord<br/>and external negative influences. This setup creates a unified shield for<br/>family unity and safety within your home.</p>"
        }
      },
      "fengshui-harmony-section": {
        "type": "fengshui-harmony-section",
        "settings": {
          "title": "Harmony  Guardian Vortex",
