      "fengshui-celestial-section-2": {
        "type": "fengshui-celestial-section-2",
        "settings": {
          "title": "Wisdom & Inspiration Formation",
          "bg_image": "shopify://shop_images/bj.jpg",
          "content": "<p><strong>Foundation: </strong>Place the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Bagua Sand Tray</em></span> on your desk or study area. Its grid<br/>harmonizes and focuses energy for mental pursuits. </p><p></p><p><strong>Southeast (Wisdom & Knowledge): </strong>Position the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Brass Wisdom Pagoda</em></span> prominently in the tray's Southeast<br/>sector. This activates academic success, concentration, and intellectual<br/>growth. </p><p></p><p><strong>Northeast (Skill & Wisdom): </strong>Place the <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Lapis Lazuli Crystal ( Angel<br/>Communication Stone)</em></span> in the tray's Northeast sector. Its deep<br/>blue energy stimulates clear thinking, insight, and access to inner wisdom. </p><p></p><p><strong>Central Support:</strong> Place the pen container with four pens<br/>upright in the central zone of the tray. This grounds the formation and<br/>represents constant access to creativity and expression. Keep the pens ready<br/>for use. </p><p></p><p><strong>Activation: </strong>Regularly touch the Pagoda while setting<br/>study goals. Hold the Lapis Lazuli during deep thinking sessions. Use the pens<br/>actively. </p><p></p><p><strong>Essence: </strong>The<br/><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><em>Bagua<br/>sand tray</em></span> integrates the space. The Southeast<br/>Pagoda enhances academic focus, while the Northeast Lapis Lazuli sparks<br/>profound insight. The central pens ensure that creative energy flows. Together,<br/>these elements create a powerful environment for sharpened intellect,<br/>inspiration, and academic achievement.</p>"
        }
      },
      "fengshui-celestial-section-3": {
        "type": "fengshui-celestial-section-3",
        "settings": {
          "title": "Celestial Orbit Series",
          "bg_image": "shopify://shop_images/bj.jpg",
          "content": "<p><strong>Core: </strong>Setup<br/>Set up the Bagua Sand Tray, which is divided into Yin (black magnetic sand) and<br/>Yang (red cinnabar sand) zones. </p><p><strong>Four Guardians: </strong></p><p><strong>East: </strong>Brass<br/>Azure Dragon with moss agate and a bamboo shoot (activates spring growth). </p><p><strong>South:</strong><br/>Brass Phoenix on a red jasper disc with pomegranate flowers (fuels summer<br/>vitality). </p><p><strong>West:</strong><br/>Brass Pi Yao facing the door, stepping on pyrite and holding an amber coin<br/>(harvests autumn wealth). </p><p><strong>North:</strong><br/>Brass Turtle carrying snow obsidian and a moonlit water bowl (anchors winter<br/>wisdom). </p><p></p><p><strong>Seasonal Nodes: </strong></p><p><strong>Southeast:</strong><br/>Madagascar ruby with a willow twig (represents blood/life energy). </p><p><strong>Southwest:</strong><br/>Pink crystal vase with lotus and gold sand (symbolizes love/harmony). </p><p><strong>Northwest: </strong>Peach-blossom<br/>incense holder with rice-pattern silk (relates to career/resources).</p><p><strong>Northeast：</strong>Lapis lazuli under a mountain stone with<br/>cotton \"snow\" (denotes stability/knowledge). </p><p></p><p><strong>Central Axis:</strong> A Brass Wen Chang Pagoda pierces the<br/>Yin-Yang symbol and is inscribed with seasonal symbols: </p><p>✸ Spring: Dragon’s palta<br/>powder </p><p>✸ Summer: Phoenix’s feather </p><p>✸ Autumn: Pi Yao’s gold- essence </p><p>✸ Winter: Turtle’s shell imprint </p><p></p><p><strong>Activation Rituals </strong></p><p>Solstices/Equinoxes: Rotate the tray 180°<br/>for spring and autumn. </p><p>Summer time: Place a clear quartz crystal<br/>atop the Brass Phoenix for 3 hours (11AM ~ 2PM)</p><p>Winter time: Place a moonstone chip atop<br/>the Turtle overnight (dusk to dawn)</p><p></p><p><strong>Daily Cycle: </strong></p><p>Dawn: Touch the Dragon for a career<br/>boost. </p><p>Noon: Face the Phoenix to attract<br/>opportunities. </p><p>Dusk: Turn the Pi Yao to secure wealth. </p><p>Night: Tap the Turtle to ensure<br/>protection.</p>"
        }
      },
      "fengshui-about-section": {
        "type": "fengshui-about-section",
        "settings": {
          "title": "Fortune & Career Flow Formation",
          "bg_image": "shopify://shop_images/bj.jpg",
          "bg_color": "#f9f5f0",
          "content_image": "shopify://shop_images/10.jpg",
          "content_text": "<p>At Puzzle Zen, we recognize that every<br/>home tells a story and holds the power to transform the lives within it. Our<br/>why is simple yet profound: to help you create a nurturing environment that<br/>channels peace and prosperity. We believe achieving harmony at home is a<br/>personal journey. Our mission is to offer a diverse selection of Feng Shui<br/>elements, enabling you to create an arrangement that aligns with your<br/>individual energy.</p>"
        }
      },
      "fengshui-about-section-2": {
        "type": "fengshui-about-section-2",
        "settings": {
          "title": "",
          "content": "<p><strong>About Us: Puzzle Zen - Piece Together Your Perfect Energy</strong></p><p>At Puzzle Zen, we recognize that every home tells a story and holds the power to<br/>transform the lives within it. Our why is simple yet profound: to help you<br/>create a nurturing environment that channels peace and prosperity. We believe<br/>achieving harmony at home is a personal journey. Our mission is to offer a<br/>diverse selection of Feng Shui elements, enabling you to create an arrangement<br/>that aligns with your individual energy.</p><p><strong>Our Story: The First Piece of the Puzzle</strong></p><p>The first piece of our puzzle was laid by our founder, Mollie Yang. With a degree<br/>in Landscape Architecture from San Francisco and 7 years in the building<br/>industry, she observed a powerful truth: the design and energy of a home<br/>directly shape the lives of those within it. It was during a visit to a<br/>friend’s cramped apartment in the city, where the afternoon light barely<br/>pierced through the cluttered decor, that an idea took root. In envisioning the<br/>space transformed into a serene haven, Mollie felt the undeniable energy shift<br/>that could result—an insight that set the foundation for Puzzle Zen.</p><p>This<br/>insight sparked a quest to move beyond traditional design and explore the<br/>ancient art of Feng Shui. Mollie wondered: if everyone's energy is different,<br/>why are Feng Shui solutions so often one-size-fits-all? This question became<br/>the cornerstone of Puzzle Zen.</p><p><strong>Our<br/>Expert Team: Your Guides to the Puzzle</strong></p><p>To support your journey, we have assembled a team of experienced professionals:</p><p>•Our Feng Shui Architect specializes in conducting in-depth home energy checkups.<br/>Using a unique approach, they assess your space to spot areas where energy is blocked and identify opportunities, providing a straightforward plan for<br/>achieving harmony in your environment.<br/><br/>•Our Destiny Analyst is an expert in the logical and precise Northern School I<br/>Ching. They help us understand the puzzle of you—your personal energy<br/>blueprint—ensuring the pieces we recommend fit your life's path and<br/>aspirations.<br/><br/></p><p><strong>Under our founder's architectural guidance, this team works together to provide you<br/>with a clear and personalized plan.</strong></p>"
        }
      },
